Charles Dechamps https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Dechamps 0 Charles Dechamps (13 September 1882 - 25 September 1959) was a French stage and film actor. He married the comedian Fernande Albany on 19 November 1925. After he died in 1959, he was buried at cimetière du Père-Lachaise.
